rComments: L'enseignement est monotone, il fait seulement lire ses notes de cours. Par contre, les exemples qu'il fait en classe sont très semblables aux numéros d'examens (parfois les mêmes mais avec des valeurs différentes). Seulement à faire les numéros c'est très possible de bien réussir! J'ai ouvert mon livre une seule fois, il n'est vraiment pas utile

Si tu veux vraiment réussir le cours, tu réuissiras.  Cependant, l'enseignement du professeur est vraiment monotone et même si je pense passer le cours, je ne crois pas que j'ai vraiment appris quoi que ce soit.  Si vous maitrisé l'anglais, prennez le cours en anglais!
Good professor, knows his stuff very well. His classes aren't very stimulating, but if you go to all of them and pay attention, there's no way you can do bad in this course.

The people here giving him bad reviews are the people that don't pay attention in class (90% of the class). If you pay attention all class every class, its impossible to do badly! If you skip most classes and fall asleep in those you go to, obviously you will have a hard time passing. Amazing prof.

Class very hard, but he was a good teacher. Soft spoken which makes it annoying when others didn't respect him and let him speak. Knew subject material very well. Helpful whenever I had any questions. I lived in that office. Even though I didn't get a great mark, I knew I tried hard and so did he. He wrote me a reference letter for a job! haha
I don't know how I got an A-. That's all I have to say
Very not clear in French nor in English. Try to take another professor for the classes he's teaching (such as taking CHM2532 in English instead).
